      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is overall very clean, though you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with all electronic features and climate control working as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid and reliable, offering a smooth ride with a documented service history that ensures it is ready for the road.",
