    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exemplary vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to a rigorous standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the cabin remains in an immaculate, factory-fresh state. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new unit, reflecting a history of uncompromising stewardship. This is a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning collector who demands absolute excellence.",
